abstract: David Allen reviews performance by pianist Behzod Abduraimov at Washington Irving High School in Manhattan, part of People's Symphony series.
lead_paragraph: In demeanor and musicianship alike, Mr. Abduraimov is no-nonsense, yet never nondescript.

headline.main: Review: Behzod Abduraimov, at People’s Symphony, Gives Each Note Its Due
headline.print_headline: With Calm and Clarity, a Young Pianist Gives Each Note Its Due and No More

snippet: In demeanor and musicianship alike, Mr. Abduraimov is no-nonsense, yet never nondescript.
